com.ibm.team.repository.common.query.ast

Interface IDateTimeField

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDateTime, IField, IFilterElement, ISelectionElement

    public interface IDateTimeField
extends IField, IDateTime
    Defines the query model for all DateTime attributes. IDateTimeField instances can be acquired by traversing to a DateTime attribute from a from a query model root.
    Since:
    0.5
